sun.jvm.hotspot.types.basic

Class BasicJIntField

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.jvm.hotspot.types.basic.BasicField
      • sun.jvm.hotspot.types.basic.BasicJIntField
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Field, JIntField

    public class BasicJIntField
extends BasicField
implements JIntField
    A specialization of Field which represents a field containing a Java int value (in either a C/C++ data structure or a Java object) and which adds typechecked getValue() routines returning ints.
